name: AXLiveAudioGraph
desc: An object that represents an audio graph for a live-updating, continuous data series for VoiceOver.

items.name: class func start()
items.desc: Begins the live audio graph session.

items.name: class func stop()
items.desc: Ends the live audio graph session.

items.name: class func updateValue(Double)
items.desc: Sets the pitch of the audio graph's tone.
